data.description: Handsome 3Bedroom 2Badroom home with massive fenced backyardis move-in ready and a waiting new Owners.Want Land? this charmer has it.A lot with huge backyard to realize your dreams with a spacious and beautiful enclosed porch,Jacuzzi outside and big outdoor Ranch wood Storage Shed.Driveway for 2 car garage there is plentyfor parking.Enjoy the out doors within the beautiful 6'Vinyl and Wood privacy Fence. This one story home shows so much pride in ownership.Excellent location,location, location. The Roof was replaced in 2021 and the Kitchen has been modernized with new smoke extractor,good appliances and granite counter tops. Also the plumbing has been updated(Re-Pipe),New garage door and new Rain gutters.Brand new painting inside and Outside.
